column5: hi everyone its shawn here,it sure has been along time since i have posted,but i do check in from time to time im still living up near bobcaygeon and fishing,as a matter of fact i met up with big cliff yesterday on the lake crappy fishing,and said hi and we chatted for a bit. i wish i could be online alot more as our puter at work is all blocked and i dont have one at home,but i now see ya can get the OFC mobile on my blackberry so i will try it out.anyway i hope everyone is doing ok and i will hopefully be able to post again like normal....take care talk soon    shawn    tightlines.....

It was nice seeing you again yesterday Shawn, too bad you had to leave so early but if it makes you feel any better, I fished until about 6:30 and the fishing didn't improve much. Too many boats running through I think.  take care, glad to see you posting again.  Cliff
Good having you back Shawn, I wondered where you were.
Ya, hope you can post more Shawn!  Fishing was your life for a long time obviously, your input was always spot on.
Good to hear from you, Shawn! Don't be a stranger!
Hey Shawn good to hear from you it's been a long time hope every thing is going good for you
Nice to see you here Shawn.  I was wondering what happened to you.  Glad to hear all is well.  Joey
Good to hear from you Shawn.Hope everything is going well.Dont be a stranger there is always a seat in my boat for you. Dan
